{
  "stem": "5740.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband got a job on the German consulate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the Austrian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Austrian-- on the Austrian consulate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's his story, so--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He worked for them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never, never went to Vienna in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was going to the Red Cross and here and there to contact his mother, his sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His sister was-- one sister was in Australia, and one-- and his mother and his other sister were in America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after months and months, we got in touch with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was a--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we decided that we'd go wherever we go-- wherever we get the, the permit or the affidavit first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, we'd go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got the permit to Australia, so we were lucky enough to come here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I met my cousins in Waldenburg--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they already knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of my cousins went back to the city in Tomashov with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, I got the confirmation that my, my brother died of typhoid on that and that day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why I'm able, every day, to, to put a candle on, on his yahrzeit--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to know when his yahrzeit is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have a date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother's date, that yahrzeit I made at Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Waited.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband was earning quite good money, because he was going to Vienna to get naturalization papers for some Germans which lost them, you know, from Austria, which lost them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was his job, going backwards and forwards to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never went to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we lived on the Austrian consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
